data.description:
Located in highly sought after SW Visalia, this charming 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offers a warm and inviting retreat for you to call your own. Step inside to discover a spacious living area adorned with natural light, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests.

Unwind in the comfort of two generously sized bedrooms, each providing ample space for rest and rejuvenation. The master bedroom boasts its own en-suite bathroom, offering a touch of privacy and accessibility.

Love to spend time outdoors? You'll adore the expansive patio area, ideal for soaking up the sun or enjoying alfresco dining with loved ones. Beyond the patio lies a quaint backyard oasis, complete with a lovely garden where you can cultivate your green thumb and immerse yourself in nature's beauty.

Parking is a breeze with the convenience of an attached 2 car garage, providing plenty of space for your vehicles and additional storage needs.

Whether you are a first-time homebuyer, an Investor or Downsizing. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful home yours! Schedule a viewing today and experience the cozy charm and convenience it has to offer.
